                </ex_als></span> <img src="imag/FRdrapeau.png"/><span class="ex_fr"><ex_fr>le matin</ex_fr></span> <img src="imag/DEdrapeau.png"/><span class="ex_de"><ex_de>am Morgen</ex_de></span>
               
