<td>proche de en</td>
<td>Kàtz, Mànn</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>ä</td>
<td>ɛ</td>
<td>è</td>
<td>Bäck, Blätt</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>e</td>
<td></td>
<td>selon le cas,<br>è ou é</td>
<td>denn, Regel</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>è</td>
<td>ɛ</td>
