<td>i</td>
<td>wiss, Zitt</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>ì</td>
<td>e</td>
<td>é</td>
<td>ìch, dìck, Kìnd, Ìgel</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>o</td>
